<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>Allgemeine Themen, Erl=C3=A4uterungen und&nbsp; Vertiefung von Aufgaben:=
&nbsp;<a href=3D"/wiki/spaces/SW/pages/329745929/Know-how+Transfer" data-li=
nked-resource-id=3D"329745929" data-linked-resource-version=3D"74" data-lin=
ked-resource-type=3D"page">Know-how Transfer</a></p>
</div>
